            <h4> Benefits of using electric vehicles </h4>
            <p> Electric cars offer a range of financial,
                performance and environmental benefits 
                when compared with internal combustion engine vehicles.
                </p>
                <br> So what are the advantages of electric cars? They are often:<br>
                <ul>
                <li> Greener. </li>
                <li> Faster. </li>
                <li> Cheap to run. </li>
                <li> More convenient to own. </li>
                <li> Soon to be cheaper to buy or lease. </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                <p> Investing in an Electric Vehicle is a smart move
                as EV's are low maintanence which means you will not
                be spending a lot of money in the car service and 
                electricity is way cheaper than gas or diesel so 
                your investment will even save you money as you 
                are saving the planet.
                </p>
            </article>
        </section>

